item.title: 【Albums (lossless)】FLAC - WayV - Give Me That - The 5th Mini Album (FLAC 24bits/96kHz)
item.description:
Give Me That is the fifth mini album by WayV. It was released on June 3, 2024 with "Give Me That" serving as the album's title track.



Member Winwin did not participate in this comeback due to schedule conflicts with his drama filming in China.[1]

The physical album comes in 13 versions: two Photobook versions, Box, five individual digipack versions, and five individual SMini versions.



Track list
  1. "Give Me That" - 2:56
  2. "She A Wolf" - 3:15
  3. "Might As Well (预言)" - 3:06
  4. "New Ride (浪漫公)" - 2:56
